# PLACEHOLDER

This file is a placeholder for the AES-256-GCM-encrypted held-out partition.
Real encryption will be applied by `generation_scripts/seal_held_out.py`
during the final run on Day 7. Until then, the unsealed JSONL lives in
`held_out/tasks.jsonl.local` (gitignored) on the trainee's local machine.

Run `python generation_scripts/verify_held_out_seal.py` to verify the
sha256 of the locally-unsealed file matches `tasks.sha256`.
